88","1376":"1376","1387":"1387","1354":"1354","1419":"1419","Paston, Norfolk, England":"Paston, Norfolk, Inglaterra","lifeSummary":"Quando Clement de Paston II nasceu em 1355, em Paston, Norfolk, Inglaterra, United Kingdom, seu pai, William de Paston, tinha 29 anos e sua mãe, Elizabeth Staleham, tinha 30 anos. Ele casou-se com Beatrice de Somerton em 1374, em Paston, Norfolk, Inglaterra. Eles tiveram pelo menos 1 filho e 2 filhas. Ele faleceu em 21 de setembro de 1388, em sua cidade natal, com 33 anos, e foi sepultado em Paston, Norfolk, Inglaterra."},"ro":{"1355–21 September 1388":"1355–21 septembrie 1388","1355–1388":"1355–1388","1357–Female":"1357–Decedată","1360–Female":"1360–Decedată","1354–1419":"1354–1419","1376–1443":"1376–1443","1378–1444":"1378–1444","1387–1488":"1387–1488","1326–1393":"1326–1393","1325–1393":"1325–1393","1374":"1374","ABT 1378":"aproximativ 1378","1382":"1382","1393":"1393","1360":"1360","1326":"1326","1325":"1325","21 September 1388":"21 septembrie 1388","1357":"1357","1488":"1488","1444":"1444","1378":"1378","1355":"1355","1443":"1443","1388":"1388","1376":"1376","1387":"1387","1354":"1354","1419":"1419","Paston, Norfolk, England":"Paston, Norfolk, England"},"ru":{"1355–21 September 1388":"1355 г.–21 сентября 1388 г.","1355–1388":"1355г.–1388г.","1357–Female":"1357г.–Умершая","1360–Female":"1360г.–Умершая","1354–1419":"1354г.–1419г.","1376–1443":"1376г.–1443г.","1378–1444":"1378г.–1444г.","1387–1488":"1387г.–1488г.","1326–1393":"1326г.–1393г.","1325–1393":"1325г.–1393г.","1374":"1374 г.","ABT 1378":"около 1378 г.","1382":"1382 г.","1393":"1393 г.","1360":"1360 г.","1326":"1326 г.","1325":"1325 г.","21 September 1388":"21 сентября 1388 г.","1357":"1357 г.","1488":"1488 г.","1444":"1444 г.","1378":"1378 г.","1355":"1355 г.","1443":"1443 г.","1388":"1388 г.","1376":"1376 г.","1387":"1387 г.","1354":"1354 г.","1419":"1419 г.","Paston, Norfolk, England":"пастон, норфолк, Англия","lifeSummary":"Когда Clement de Paston II родился в 1355 г. в местности пастон, норфолк, Англия, Великобритания, его отцу по имени William de Paston было 29 лет, а матери, которую звали Elizabeth Staleham, 30. Он женился на женщине по имени Beatrice de Somerton в 1374 г. в местности пастон, норфолк, Англия. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын и 2 дочери. Он умер 21 сентября 1388 г. в его родном городе в возрасте 33 лет и был похоронен в местности пастон, норфолк, Англия."},"sm":{"1355–21 September 1388":"1355–21 Setema 1388","1355–1388":"1355–1388","1357–Female":"1357–Ua Maliu","1360–Female":"1360–Ua Maliu","1354–1419":"1354–1419","1376–1443":"1376–1443","1378–1444":"1378–1444","1387–1488":"1387–1488","1326–1393":"1326–1393","1325–1393":"1325–1393","1374":"1374","ABT 1378":"e tusa o le 1378","1382":"1382","1393":"1393","1360":"1360","1326":"1326","1325":"1325","21 September 1388":"21 Setema 1388","1357":"1357","1488":"1488","1444":"1444","1378":"1378","1355":"1355","1443":"1443","1388":"1388","1376":"1376","1387":"1387","1354":"1354","1419":"1419","Paston, Norfolk, England":"Paston, Norfolk, Egelani"},"sk":{"1355–21 September 1388":"1355–21. september 1388","1355–1388":"1355–1388","1357–Female":"1357–Zosnulá","1360–Female":"1360–Zosnulá","1354–1419":"1354–1419","1376–1443":"1376–1443","1378–1444":"1378–1444","1387–1488":"1387–1488","1326–1393":"1326–1393","1325–1393":"1325–1393","1374":"1374","ABT 1378":"okolo 1378","1382":"1382","1393":"1393","1360":"1360","1326":"1326","1325":"1325","21 September 1388":"21. september 1388","1357":"1357","1488":"1488","1444":"1444","1378":"1378","1355":"1355","1443":"1443","1388":"1388","1376":"1376","1387":"1387","1354":"1354","1419":"1419","Paston, Norfolk, England":"Paston, Norfolk, England"},"es":{"1355–21 September 1388":"1355–21 de septiembre de 1388","1355–1388":"1355–1388","1357–Female":"1357–Fallecida","1360–Female":"1360–Fallecida","1354–1419":"1354–1419","1376–1443":"1376–1443","1378–1444":"1378–1444","1387–1488":"1387–1488","1326–1393":"1326–1393","1325–1393":"1325–1393","1374":"1374",